data.description: Sought after but seldom available 3 Bedroom, 2 bath ranch home on a level lot. Meticulously maintained this lovely home features the following:  Split bedroom plan, Open floor plan w/family room and dining area, fireplace, Large Master bedroom with large walk-in closet, spacious secondary bedrooms. Roof was replaced three years ago, New Water Heater 2021, New HVAC 2021. Bridgemill is a golf, swim, tennis/pickle ball community with Featherstones Restaurant inside the clubhouse. Close to shopping, restaurants, bike trails, and highways. Great home, attractive price, fantastic neighborhood, and award winning schools!
